.SH NAME
vapi-tool - Manage Vapi tools and functions


.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBvapi tool [flags]\fP


.SH DESCRIPTION
Manage custom tools and functions that connect your voice agents to external APIs and databases.

.PP
Tools enable your assistants to:
- Call external APIs and web services
- Access databases and business systems
- Perform custom actions during conversations
- Integrate with third-party platforms
- Execute business logic and workflows


